quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,59,"Pellet, Darngal, ngal Allah wuurnitata maay…ìe …ìen e mun, fii √±aawugol …ìe yo…ìa, ko ko arata, feere mun alaa, sikka alaa e …óum. Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe gom…óinaa …óum. Ko …óum ha…ói …ìe hebilanagol nden √±alnde"
  40,60,"Joomi mon, onon yim…ìe …ìen, daali: heertinanee Lam, Min tun, dewal e toraare, Mi jaabinana on toraare mon, Mi yawtana on, Mi yurmina on. Mawnintinantoo…ìe …óum …ìen, ko pellet, √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe naatoyay Jahannama, ko …ìe hoy…ìe jaasinaa."
  40,61,"Ko Allah woni wa…óiran…óo on jemma on, ni…ì…ìitir…óo, fii ka dee∆¥on fowto…óon e mun, O wa…óirani on nyalorma on, ndaygin…óo, fii ka gollon e mun. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ìural mawngal e yim…ìe …ìen, tawde O timminirii neemaaji Makko …óin e ma…ì…ìe, no fee√±iri e no wirnori. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, …ìe yettataa Allah, e naamaaji Makko …óin, dow ma…ì…ìe."
  40,62,"Ko On moo…óon Allah, wa…óan…óo on …óin neemaaji, woni Tagu…óo kala huunde. Wanaa go…ó…óo goo. Rewtee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Ko honno ferlisora…óon gaay e rewugol Mo, jokka rewugol ko nafataa lorrataa?"
  40,63,"Ko wano …ìee …óoo ferlisoraa non e gom…óingol Allah rewa Mo Kanko tun, …ìeya yeddaynoo…ìe Aayeeje Allah tindinay…ói fii tawhiidi on, ferlisortenoo e kala jamaanu, …ìe feewataano e goonga, …ìe hawrataano e sawaaba."
  40,64,"Ko Allah woni wa…óan…óo on, onon yim…ìe …ìen, ndii leydi, dunngal √±ii…ìirgal mon, O wa…ói kammu ngun, √±e√±aangu dow mon, hara yanataa e mon, O mbaadini on ka renngaaji yumma mon'en - O mo∆¥∆¥ini mbaadiiji mon, - O arsiki on laa…ìu…ói dagii…ói. Ko On moo…óon, neeminir…óo on …óum, woni Allah Joomi mon. Senaare heewii e Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow. Rewetee…óo alanaa ngo, si wanaa Kanko senii…óo On."
  40,65,"Ko Kanko woni wuur…óo Mo maayataa On. rewetee…óo e goonga alaa, si wanaa Kanko. Noddiree Mo dewal e toraare; faando…óon Mo Kanko tun, hara on kafidaali Mo e taguuji Makko goo. Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tageefo ngon."
  40,66,"Maaku an Nulaa…óo: min, Allah ha…óii lam rewugol, …óin …ói rewoton, hara wanaa Allah; sanamuuji …ói nafataa, …ói lorrataa. Mi ha…óa …óum, nde hujjaaji …óin arunoo e am, fii …ìanngingol meere rewugol …óin. Allah yamiri lam kadi, nde mi jebbilantoo Mo, Kanko tun, ka dewal. Tawde ko Kanko woni Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow. Jey…óo ngo alaa, si wanaa Kanko."